OL,3,C'Everyone has a heart, it's just our
OL,4,Cjob to try and save it'
OL,6,FAmy Sutton has been finding out how
OL,7,Fone dad's mission to give back after
OL,8,Fhis daughter's life-saving heart
OL,9,Fsurgery is paying off
OL,11,FA father inspired by the life-saving
OL,12,Fopen heart surgery performed on his
OL,13,Ftwo-year-old daughter is continuing to
OL,14,Fhelp give others a second chance of
OL,15,Flife.
OL,17,FSergio Petrucci, from Sunderland, set
OL,18,Fup a cardiac care charity in a bid to
OL,19,Fshow his thanks to the medical
OL,20,Fprofessionals who operated on his
OL,21,Fdaughter Luna in 2015.
