OL,6,FOne of four ITV News Tyne Tees
OL,7,Ffinalists for the Daily Mirror Pride
OL,8,Fof Britain Regional Fundraiser of the
OL,9,FYear award, Mr Petrucci later set up
OL,10,FThe Red Sky Foundation which has
OL,11,Fraised millions of pounds and provided
OL,12,Fhundreds of defibrillators in the
OL,13,Fcommunity.
OL,15,F"I don't really understand how it got
OL,16,Fso big," he told ITV Tyne Tees. "I was
OL,17,Falways passionate about raising the
OL,18,Ffunds for buying machinery and
OL,19,Fequipment and making an impact.
