OL,3,C'Everyone has a heart, it's just our
OL,4,Cjob to try and save it'
OL,6,FMr Petrucci's daughter Luna was born
OL,7,Fwith two holes in her heart. Just
OL,8,Fbefore her second birthday, doctors
OL,9,Fsaid it was now or never - she needed
OL,10,Fopen heart surgery.
OL,12,FOn the morning Luna was wheeled off
OL,13,Ffor treatment at Newcastle's Freeman
OL,14,FHospital, the sky blazed red -
OL,15,Finspiring the name of the charity the
OL,16,Ffather would go on to found with his
OL,17,Fwife Emma in 2020.
