OL,6,FIt has since raised more than #2m,
OL,7,Fdonated more than 700 defibrillators,
OL,8,Ffunded machines that have conducted in
OL,9,Fexcess of 800 brain and heart scans
OL,10,Fevery year, and educated people of all
OL,11,Fages on the importance of CPR.
OL,13,FFive years down the line and its work
OL,14,Fis still paying off - giving others
OL,15,Fthat vital second chance at life.
OL,17,FThree years ago, a healthy Craig
OL,18,FHanson suffered cardiac arrest and
OL,19,Fcollapsed in his own home.
