OL,6,FA neighbour rushed to his aid and
OL,7,Fdelivered CPR - another fetching a
OL,8,Fnearby defibrillator - funded by Mr
OL,9,FPetrucci - which ultimately saved his
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,F"I received two blasts from the
OL,13,Fmachine and it restarted my heart,"
OL,14,Fsaid Mr Hanson.
OL,16,F"I wasn't really aware, although I
OL,17,Fmust have walked past that
OL,18,Fdefibrillator hundreds of times, and
OL,19,Fnot realised the importance of it -
OL,20,Fnow obviously I do."
